<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Helix-Swarm — Local-First CLI Agent Swarm</title>
  <meta
    name="description"
    content="Helix-Swarm is a local-first CLI agent swarm with safe tool approval, SkillHub integration, evidence-based review, and Gemma 4 thinking."
  />

  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #070a12;
      --bg-soft: #0b1020;
      --card: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.075);
      --card-strong: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.11);
      --border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
      --text: #eef4ff;
      --muted: #9aa9c2;
      --cyan: #22d3ee;
      --blue: #60a5fa;
      --green: #22c55e;
      --yellow: #f59e0b;
      --purple: #a78bfa;
      --red: #fb7185;
      --shadow: 0 30px 90px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
      --radius: 26px;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 15% 8%, rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.20), transparent 32%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 85% 10%, rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.18), transparent 32%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 95%, rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.12), transparent 35%),
        var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family:
        Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont,
        "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .noise {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      opacity: 0.08;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 48px 48px;
      mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, black, transparent 80%);
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .orb {
      position: fixed;
      width: 520px;
      height: 520px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      filter: blur(80px);
      opacity: 0.35;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .orb.one {
      top: -180px;
      left: -120px;
      background: #22d3ee;
    }

    .orb.two {
      top: 140px;
      right: -220px;
      background: #8b5cf6;
    }

    .orb.three {
      bottom: -260px;
      left: 35%;
      background: #22c55e;
      opacity: 0.18;
    }

    .page {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .container {
      width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 40px));
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .nav {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 20;
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      background: rgba(7, 10, 18, 0.72);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    }

    .nav-inner {
      height: 72px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .brand-mark {
      width: 38px;
      height: 38px;
      border-radius: 13px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background:
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.9), rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.9));
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.24);
      color: #05121d;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 18px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .lang-toggle {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      padding: 6px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    }

    .lang-toggle button {
      border: 0;
      cursor: pointer;
      padding: 7px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: var(--muted);
      background: transparent;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .lang-toggle button.active {
      color: #05121d;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cyan), var(--green));
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 92px 0 70px;
    }

    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.08fr 0.92fr;
      gap: 44px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 9px 14px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.25);
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.08);
      color: #b7f7ff;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    .pulse {
      width: 9px;
      height: 9px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--green);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 8px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.12);
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(44px, 7vw, 84px);
      line-height: 0.95;
      letter-spacing: -0.07em;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .gradient-text {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff, #b7f7ff 42%, #c4b5fd);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      color: transparent;
    }

    .hero-copy {
      max-width: 680px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 19px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 34px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 14px 20px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      font-weight: 800;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, border 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .btn.primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cyan), var(--green));
      color: #05121d;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.2);
    }

    .btn.secondary {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .badges {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .badge {
      padding: 8px 11px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: var(--muted);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.045);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .terminal-card {
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.11), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.055));
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      overflow: hidden;
      transform: perspective(900px) rotateY(-4deg) rotateX(2deg);
    }

    .terminal-top {
      height: 52px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0 18px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.10);
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.22);
    }

    .dots {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .dot {
      width: 12px;
      height: 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
    }

    .dot.red { background: #fb7185; }
    .dot.yellow { background: #facc15; }
    .dot.green { background: #22c55e; }

    .terminal-title {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .terminal-body {
      padding: 22px;
      font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, "Liberation Mono", monospace;
      font-size: 13.5px;
      min-height: 420px;
    }

    .line {
      margin: 8px 0;
      color: #dbeafe;
    }

    .prompt {
      color: var(--cyan);
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .muted {
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .green {
      color: #86efac;
    }

    .yellow {
      color: #fde68a;
    }

    .purple {
      color: #c4b5fd;
    }

    .panel {
      margin: 18px 0;
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.28);
      background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.08);
    }

    .section {
      padding: 70px 0;
    }

    .section-head {
      max-width: 760px;
      margin-bottom: 34px;
    }

    .section-kicker {
      color: var(--cyan);
      font-weight: 900;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      font-size: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 52px);
      line-height: 1.05;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .section-text {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .grid.cols-3 {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }

    .grid.cols-2 {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .feature-card,
    .glass-card {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 22px;
      padding: 24px;
      background: var(--card);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);
    }

    .feature-icon {
      width: 46px;
      height: 46px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      background: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.22);
      font-size: 22px;
    }

    .feature-card h3,
    .glass-card h3 {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .feature-card p,
    .glass-card p {
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .architecture {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      overflow: hidden;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    }

    .arch-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 220px 1fr;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    }

    .arch-row:last-child {
      border-bottom: 0;
    }

    .arch-label {
      padding: 22px;
      color: #b7f7ff;
      font-weight: 900;
      background: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.06);
      border-right: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    }

    .arch-content {
      padding: 22px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .code {
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.34);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      overflow-x: auto;
      color: #dbeafe;
      font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, monospace;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .steps {
      counter-reset: step;
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .step {
      position: relative;
      padding: 22px 22px 22px 76px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: var(--card);
    }

    .step::before {
      counter-increment: step;
      content: counter(step);
      position: absolute;
      left: 22px;
      top: 20px;
      width: 34px;
      height: 34px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cyan), var(--green));
      color: #041018;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .step h3 {
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .step p {
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .roadmap {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .roadmap-item {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: flex-start;
      padding: 16px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.055);
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .check {
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      flex: 0 0 auto;
      background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.13);
      color: #86efac;
      border: 1px solid rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.25);
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .todo {
      background: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.13);
      color: #bfdbfe;
      border-color: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.25);
    }

    .cta {
      margin: 70px 0 40px;
      padding: 46px;
      border-radius: 34px;
      background:
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.18), rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.16)),
        rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .cta h2 {
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .cta p {
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 0 auto 24px;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    footer {
      padding: 34px 0 60px;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    [data-lang="zh"] {
      display: none;
    }

    body.zh [data-lang="en"] {
      display: none;
    }

    body.zh [data-lang="zh"] {
      display: initial;
    }

    body.zh div[data-lang="zh"],
    body.zh section[data-lang="zh"],
    body.zh p[data-lang="zh"] {
      display: block;
    }

    @media (max-width: 920px) {
      .nav-links {
        display: none;
      }

      .hero-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .terminal-card {
        transform: none;
      }

      .grid.cols-3,
      .grid.cols-2 {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .arch-row {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .arch-label {
        border-right: 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      }

      .hero {
        padding-top: 58px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="orb one"></div>
  <div class="orb two"></div>
  <div class="orb three"></div>
  <div class="noise"></div>

  <div class="page">
    <nav class="nav">
      <div class="container nav-inner">
        <a class="brand" href="#top">
          <span class="brand-mark">H</span>
          <span>Helix-Swarm</span>
        </a>

        <div class="nav-links">
          <a href="#features">Features</a>
          <a href="#architecture">Architecture</a>
          <a href="#install">Install</a>
          <a href="#roadmap">Roadmap</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/Yule-Cai/Helix-Swarm" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">GitHub</a>
        </div>

        <div class="lang-toggle" aria-label="Language switcher">
          <button id="btn-en" class="active" onclick="setLang('en')">EN</button>
          <button id="btn-zh" onclick="setLang('zh')">中文</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <header id="top" class="hero">
      <div class="container hero-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">
            <span class="pulse"></span>
            <span data-lang="en">Local-first CLI Agent Swarm</span>
            <span data-lang="zh">本地优先的 CLI Agent Swarm</span>
          </div>

          <h1>
            <span class="gradient-text" data-lang="en">Safe local agents for real terminal workflows.</span>
            <span class="gradient-text" data-lang="zh">面向真实终端工作流的安全本地 Agent。</span>
          </h1>

          <p class="hero-copy" data-lang="en">
            Helix-Swarm connects local models, SkillHub skills, file reading, permission-gated tool execution,
            evidence-based review, and Gemma 4 thinking into one practical CLI agent framework.
          </p>

          <p class="hero-copy" data-lang="zh">
            Helix-Swarm 将本地模型、SkillHub 技能、文件读取、工具调用审查、证据卡审查和 Gemma 4 thinking
            整合成一个实用的 CLI Agent 框架。
          </p>

          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="btn primary" href="https://github.com/Yule-Cai/Helix-Swarm" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
              <span data-lang="en">View on GitHub</span>
              <span data-lang="zh">查看 GitHub</span>
              <span>↗</span>
            </a>
            <a class="btn secondary" href="#install">
              <span data-lang="en">Quick Start</span>
              <span data-lang="zh">快速开始</span>
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="badges">
            <span class="badge">LM Studio</span>
            <span class="badge">Gemma 4 Thinking</span>
            <span class="badge">SkillHub</span>
            <span class="badge">Permission Gate</span>
            <span class="badge">Evidence Cards</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="terminal-card">
          <div class="terminal-top">
            <div class="dots">
              <span class="dot red"></span>
              <span class="dot yellow"></span>
              <span class="dot green"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="terminal-title">helix-swarm / local</div>
          </div>

          <div class="terminal-body">
            <div class="line"><span class="prompt">❯</span> /set lang en</div>
            <div class="line green">✅ UI config updated: lang = en</div>
            <div class="line"><span class="prompt">❯</span> skillhub search calendar</div>
            <div class="line muted">📋 Task type: chat</div>
            <div class="line green">✅ Low-risk query command, auto-running...</div>
            <div class="line yellow">calendar-cli · google-calendar · google-calendar-api</div>

            <div class="panel">
              <div class="line yellow">🛡️ Direct Terminal Command Review</div>
              <div class="line">Command: <span class="purple">skillhub install calendar-cli</span></div>
              <div class="line">Risk level: <span class="yellow">high</span></div>
              <div class="line muted">Y = Approve · N = Deny · B = Block</div>
            </div>

            <div class="line"><span class="prompt">❯</span> Review current project, read-only.</div>
            <div class="line green">Evidence Card 1</div>
            <div class="line muted">File: core/permission_manager.py</div>
            <div class="line muted">Symbol: _is_in_workspace()</div>
            <div class="line muted">Evidence: concrete path boundary check...</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section id="features" class="section">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="section-head">
            <div class="section-kicker">Features</div>
            <h2 data-lang="en">Built for useful local autonomy, not blind automation.</h2>
            <h2 data-lang="zh">为有用的本地自主能力而设计，不是盲目自动化。</h2>
            <p class="section-text" data-lang="en">
              Helix-Swarm gives local agents practical tool access while keeping risky actions visible and reviewable.
            </p>
            <p class="section-text" data-lang="zh">
              Helix-Swarm 让本地 Agent 能真正使用工具，同时让高风险操作保持可见、可审查。
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="grid cols-3">
            <div class="feature-card">
              <div class="feature-icon">🛡️</div>
              <h3 data-lang="en">Permission-gated tools</h3>
              <h3 data-lang="zh">工具权限审查</h3>
              <p data-lang="en">Low-risk read/search tools can be auto-approved, while install, shell, write, and delete operations require confirmation.</p>
              <p data-lang="zh">读取和搜索类低风险工具可自动允许；安装、终端、写入和删除操作需要用户确认。</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card">
              <div class="feature-icon">🧠</div>
              <h3 data-lang="en">Gemma 4 thinking</h3>
              <h3 data-lang="zh">Gemma 4 Thinking</h3>
              <p data-lang="en">Automatically detects Gemma 4-style model names and enables thinking mode while filtering reasoning from memory.</p>
              <p data-lang="zh">自动识别 Gemma 4 系列模型并开启 thinking mode，同时避免把内部推理写入记忆。</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card">
              <div class="feature-icon">📚</div>
              <h3 data-lang="en">SkillHub integration</h3>
              <h3 data-lang="zh">SkillHub 集成</h3>
              <p data-lang="en">Search, inspect, and compare skills before installation, so agents do not blindly install capabilities.</p>
              <p data-lang="zh">支持安装前搜索、检查和比较 Skill，避免 Agent 盲目安装能力。</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card">
              <div class="feature-icon">🧾</div>
              <h3 data-lang="en">Evidence Card review</h3>
              <h3 data-lang="zh">证据卡审查</h3>
              <p data-lang="en">Review tasks must cite concrete files, symbols, evidence, risk, consequence, and suggested fixes.</p>
              <p data-lang="zh">审查任务必须给出文件、函数、证据、风险、后果和修复建议。</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card">
              <div class="feature-icon">📄</div>
              <h3 data-lang="en">Local file reading</h3>
              <h3 data-lang="zh">本地文件读取</h3>
              <p data-lang="en">Detects local file paths and routes PDF, DOCX, Markdown, text, and source files into the agent workflow.</p>
              <p data-lang="zh">识别本地文件路径，并将 PDF、DOCX、Markdown、文本和源代码文件送入 Agent 流程。</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card">
              <div class="feature-icon">🌐</div>
              <h3 data-lang="en">Bilingual CLI</h3>
              <h3 data-lang="zh">中英文 CLI</h3>
              <p data-lang="en">Switch interface language with /set lang en or /set lang zh, including prompts, panels, and review templates.</p>
              <p data-lang="zh">通过 /set lang en 或 /set lang zh 切换界面语言，覆盖提示、面板和审查模板。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="architecture" class="section">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="section-head">
            <div class="section-kicker">Architecture</div>
            <h2 data-lang="en">A supervisor-agent loop with tool review.</h2>
            <h2 data-lang="zh">带工具审查的 Supervisor-Agent 循环。</h2>
            <p class="section-text" data-lang="en">
              The CLI routes commands, Leo supervises specialist agents, and the permission manager reviews risky tools.
            </p>
            <p class="section-text" data-lang="zh">
              CLI 负责路由命令，Leo 监督专家 Agent，权限管理器审查高风险工具调用。
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="architecture">
            <div class="arch-row">
              <div class="arch-label">CLI Router</div>
              <div class="arch-content" data-lang="en">Handles slash commands, direct shell command detection, task classification, and language-aware UI.</div>
              <div class="arch-content" data-lang="zh">处理 Slash 命令、直接终端命令检测、任务分类和语言感知 UI。</div>
            </div>
            <div class="arch-row">
              <div class="arch-label">Leo Supervisor</div>
              <div class="arch-content" data-lang="en">Delegates work to File Agent, Search Agent, Reviewer, and Computer Agent.</div>
              <div class="arch-content" data-lang="zh">将任务委派给 File Agent、Search Agent、Reviewer 和 Computer Agent。</div>
            </div>
            <div class="arch-row">
              <div class="arch-label">Tool Registry</div>
              <div class="arch-content" data-lang="en">Discovers Python tools and Markdown SOP skills from tools/ and skills/.</div>
              <div class="arch-content" data-lang="zh">从 tools/ 和 skills/ 中发现 Python 工具和 Markdown SOP 技能。</div>
            </div>
            <div class="arch-row">
              <div class="arch-label">Permission Manager</div>
              <div class="arch-content" data-lang="en">Reviews terminal commands, installs, file writes, edits, deletes, and dangerous shell patterns.</div>
              <div class="arch-content" data-lang="zh">审查终端命令、安装、文件写入、编辑、删除和危险 shell 模式。</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="install" class="section">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="section-head">
            <div class="section-kicker">Installation</div>
            <h2 data-lang="en">Start with a local model server.</h2>
            <h2 data-lang="zh">从本地模型服务开始。</h2>
            <p class="section-text" data-lang="en">
              Use LM Studio or any OpenAI-compatible endpoint. Then run Helix-Swarm from the terminal.
            </p>
            <p class="section-text" data-lang="zh">
              使用 LM Studio 或任何 OpenAI-compatible endpoint，然后在终端中运行 Helix-Swarm。
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="grid cols-2">
            <div class="glass-card">
              <h3 data-lang="en">Quick start</h3>
              <h3 data-lang="zh">快速开始</h3>
              <div class="code">git clone https://github.com/Yule-Cai/Helix-Swarm.git
cd Helix-Swarm
python3 -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
python3 cli.py</div>
            </div>

            <div class="glass-card">
              <h3 data-lang="en">Configure model</h3>
              <h3 data-lang="zh">配置模型</h3>
              <div class="code">/set url http://localhost:1234/v1/chat/completions
/set model google/gemma-4-e4b
/set lang en

# Switch back to Chinese
/set lang zh</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="workflow" class="section">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="section-head">
            <div class="section-kicker">Workflow</div>
            <h2 data-lang="en">Ask naturally, approve carefully.</h2>
            <h2 data-lang="zh">自然提问，谨慎确认。</h2>
          </div>

          <div class="steps">
            <div class="step">
              <h3 data-lang="en">Describe the task</h3>
              <h3 data-lang="zh">描述任务</h3>
              <p data-lang="en">Ask the CLI to read a file, compare SkillHub skills, review a project, or run a command.</p>
              <p data-lang="zh">让 CLI 读取文件、比较 SkillHub 技能、审查项目或执行命令。</p>
            </div>

            <div class="step">
              <h3 data-lang="en">Inspect tool calls</h3>
              <h3 data-lang="zh">检查工具调用</h3>
              <p data-lang="en">Safe native tools can pass automatically; risky operations are shown in a review panel.</p>
              <p data-lang="zh">安全原生工具可以自动通过；高风险操作会显示在审查面板中。</p>
            </div>

            <div class="step">
              <h3 data-lang="en">Approve or deny</h3>
              <h3 data-lang="zh">确认或拒绝</h3>
              <p data-lang="en">Press Y to approve, N to deny, or B to block the tool for the current session.</p>
              <p data-lang="zh">按 Y 确认，N 拒绝，B 禁止该工具在本会话继续调用。</p>
            </div>

            <div class="step">
              <h3 data-lang="en">Verify the result</h3>
              <h3 data-lang="zh">验证结果</h3>
              <p data-lang="en">Evidence Card review makes project audits traceable to concrete files and symbols.</p>
              <p data-lang="zh">Evidence Card 让项目审查可以追溯到具体文件和函数。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="roadmap" class="section">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="section-head">
            <div class="section-kicker">Roadmap</div>
            <h2 data-lang="en">What is next?</h2>
            <h2 data-lang="zh">下一步计划</h2>
          </div>

          <div class="roadmap">
            <div class="roadmap-item"><span class="check">✓</span><span>CLI-first local agent loop / CLI 优先的本地 Agent 主循环</span></div>
            <div class="roadmap-item"><span class="check">✓</span><span>Permission-gated terminal execution / 终端执行权限审查</span></div>
            <div class="roadmap-item"><span class="check">✓</span><span>Evidence Card review mode / 证据卡审查模式</span></div>
            <div class="roadmap-item"><span class="check">✓</span><span>Gemma 4 thinking detection / Gemma 4 thinking 自动识别</span></div>
            <div class="roadmap-item"><span class="check todo">→</span><span>/image command for vision models / 面向视觉模型的 /image 命令</span></div>
            <div class="roadmap-item"><span class="check todo">→</span><span>Unified /file pipeline for PDF, DOCX, XLSX, images, and ZIP / 统一文件管线</span></div>
            <div class="roadmap-item"><span class="check todo">→</span><span>Stronger reviewer verifier / 更强的审查验证器</span></div>
            <div class="roadmap-item"><span class="check todo">→</span><span>Optional lightweight Web UI / 可选轻量 Web UI</span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="cta">
            <h2 data-lang="en">Build safer local agents.</h2>
            <h2 data-lang="zh">构建更安全的本地 Agent。</h2>
            <p data-lang="en">
              Helix-Swarm is experimental, but already useful for local tool workflows, project review, SkillHub exploration, and terminal-assisted tasks.
            </p>
            <p data-lang="zh">
              Helix-Swarm 仍处于实验阶段，但已经可以用于本地工具工作流、项目审查、SkillHub 探索和终端辅助任务。
            </p>
            <a class="btn primary" href="https://github.com/Yule-Cai/Helix-Swarm" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
              <span data-lang="en">Open GitHub Repository</span>
              <span data-lang="zh">打开 GitHub 仓库</span>
              <span>↗</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
      MIT License · Built with ❤️ by Yule-Cai · Helix-Swarm
    </footer>
  </div>

  <script>
    function setLang(lang) {
      document.body.classList.toggle("zh", lang === "zh");
      document.documentElement.lang = lang === "zh" ? "zh-CN" : "en";
      localStorage.setItem("helix-lang", lang);

      document.getElementById("btn-en").classList.toggle("active", lang === "en");
      document.getElementById("btn-zh").classList.toggle("active", lang === "zh");
    }

    const savedLang = localStorage.getItem("helix-lang") || "en";
    setLang(savedLang);
  </script>
</body>
</html>
